snippet.title: Car Challenger - Browser game
snippet.description:
Car Challenger is a simple racing game on based motives of Trackmania. This is video from its first version which offers 3 various cars and 3 maps. The goal is to complete every map under a certain time limit.
The game is native, runs in browser and does not need any installation. 

Play the game at http://www.pacogames.com/driving/car-challenger/en
